Class ShapeImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • EObjectImpl

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArcImpl, EllipseImpl, LineImpl, RectangleImpl

    public abstract class ShapeImpl
extends FigureImpl
implements Shape
    An implementation of the model object 'Shape'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Line Width
    • Antialias
    • Alpha
    • Fill
    • Outline
